    {
      "id": "1914750c-f3ba-80e9-b765-d1e0f5c19bef",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "In social network learning, forming appropriate groups is both essential to promote an optimal learning process and time-consuming. The paper offers an approach to group formation that hinges on 3 key attributes: academic, cognitive and social components. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1914750c-f3ba-80e9-b765-d1e0f5c19bef",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
