    {
      "id": "1914750c-f3ba-80c2-9bbb-fbf57d50437c",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "These components are used on a genetic algorithm approach that uses 2 crossover operators. Results show this approach considers more parameters and is more efficient at achieving an optimal solution than standard GA. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
